<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[الطُّليان]</span>: جمع: طِلا.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فِعْلان]</span>، بكسر الفاء<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
